{"tid":834370,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"你班帶狗落街比隻狗隨地便溺既仆街","createTime":"2018-09-24T07:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T04:52:33.000Z","uid":160028,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e18428e15f263a9c06c6e790e44aade10c4ea2b6","tid":834370,"uid":160028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:08:29.000Z","msg":"琴晚八點幾落街經過一個好多人經過既街口，見到有條撚樣紋身炸手後生仔比隻狗屙撚完屎又唔鏟返地下篤屎，仆街一邊食煙一邊玩電話，比隻狗自己每一米放一粒地雷，跟住走撚左去，因為呢半年黎呢到附近總係周地踏到周圍都係既狗屎，食環署都貼哂告示話會罰錢<br />\n<br />\n跟住我急步追上去係佢後面好撚大聲講: 屌你老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你比隻狗屙完又唔整乾淨返，嚇撚到佢係咁講對唔住，我話呢到經常都有狗屎係咪你做既，條撚樣心虛到話新養隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家見到呢d仆街要英勇當面指責佢，要祝呢班友下世做食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0877e1e8896d4d3c2af445d291a6b49c76d0204","tid":834370,"uid":197563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:25:15.000Z","msg":"有兩隻食屎狗輕輕留低負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c48ccc6635374c9d3ca71a37b67358e08ebcd7e","tid":834370,"uid":160028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:26:40.000Z","msg":"呢d仆街唔可以放過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2440ea6e8d225db7fa10b90e68b3b06090cae3","tid":834370,"uid":2403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:55:34.000Z","msg":"驚俾人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a4d5c94af6f2198665b5469d1904ec014a4da9","tid":834370,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:40:27.000Z","msg":"今日行d單車徑邊  <br />\n都有2.3篤狗屎<br />\n係唔係要禁止d人放狗?<br />\